  "title": "Retail Sales Promoter (Sungei Kadut / 6 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Work towards achieving departmental sales targets and objectives</li>\n  <li>Actively promote and demonstrate products at dealer outlets</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the assigned Sales Executive to meet both individual and team sales goals</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain strong relationships with key outlet stakeholders</li>\n  <li>Handle customer inquiries and resolve complaints promptly and professionally</li>\n  <li>Monitor and report on competitor activities, pricing, and promotional campaigns</li>\n  <li>Ensure product displays and concept counters are well-maintained and visually appealing</li>\n  <li>Support departmental marketing initiatives and sales campaigns</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
